- <internalRef>, the relations between different objects in an graphic object or
multimedia object (eg, to allow that clicking one object will result in the referenced object to
be highlighted or the current view to change). Refer to Chap 3.9.5.2.1.2.
- <dmRef>. Refer to Chap 3.9.5.2.1.2.
