2.6 Special rules for marking change in figures

There are three ways to change mark a figure. By marking the individual elements, the project
gets flexibility at presentation. For the presentation of changes to figures, refer to Chap 6.2.2.
Figures can be change marked on:
- the figure only. Refer to Para 2.6.1.
- the title of a figure only. Refer to Para 2.6.2.
