2.6.1 Marking the complete figure only

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2.6.1.1 Adding
  
When a figure is added, its title is also added, because the element <title> is mandatory
within the element <figure>. Set appropriate values to the attributes of the element <figure>.

  
Markup example:

<figure id="fig-0003" changeType="add" changeMark="1" reasonForUpdateRefIds="rfu-0001">
