2.5.1.3.6 Tool reference

Description: The element <toolRef> contains the reference to support equipment
(standard tool, special tool or test equipment), for those projects that use 
a tool common information repository.

  
Markup element: <toolRef>

Attributes:
- id (O), the identifier of the markup element. Refer to Chap 3.9.5.2.1.2.
