the change indications. Refer to Chap 3.9.5.2.1.1.
- toolNumber (M), the tool part number. Used together with the attribute 
manufacturerCodeValue, as the identifier of the tool, in the tool repository
(implicit reference method). Refer to Chap 3.9.5.2.11.9.
