<embeddedSpareDescr> with the original spares removed from the Product
- If the element <spareDescr> is a simple spare provided from the store or already
present on the product, then the attribute materialUsage follows the instantiation
rules described inPara 2.7.1and there is no element <embeddedSpareDescr>

  
