2.4 Levelled paragraphs

Description: The element <levelledPara> is the equivalent of a headed paragraph 
and subparagraphs. It can have one or more <levelledPara> elements nested within it
and/or one or more <levelledParaAlts> elements. The depth of this structure 
is unlimited, however, it is recommended to not exceed five levels of depth. 
